Assume "students" is a collection


1. Update single document of collection
    db.students.update(
        { id : 10},
        { $set : { "name" : "Tohid Ahmed"}}
    )

2. Update multiple document of a collection
    db.students.update(
        { "age" : 16 },
        { $set : { status : "Big Child" }},
        {multi : true }
    )

        
